---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Accueil">

  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
      Paul, Étudiant en <span class="text-primary dark:text-blue-400">Cybersécurité</span> & <span class="text-primary dark:text-blue-400">Admin. Réseau</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Passionné par l'infrastructure et la sécurité, actuellement en BTS CIEL. 
      À la recherche d'une alternance pour contribuer à vos projets.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 space-x-4">
      <a href="/projets" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors">
        Découvrir mes projets
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
        Me contacter
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Mes Compétences Clés</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary dark:text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Systèmes & Réseaux</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Administration Linux (Ubuntu, Debian) et Windows Server. Configuration et dépannage réseau.</p>
        <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-100 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Cisco NetAcad</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary dark:text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Programmation & Scripting</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Développement en C++ pour les systèmes embarqués et Python pour l'automatisation et l'analyse.</p>
        <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 text-green-800 dark:text-green-100 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full mr-2">C++</span>
        <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900 text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-100 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Python (PCEP)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary dark:text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Cybersécurité</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Principes de sécurisation des systèmes et des réseaux, analyse de logs, et mise en place de pare-feu.</p>
        <span class="inline-block bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900 text-red-800 dark:text-red-100 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">BTS CIEL Opt. A</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .text-primary { color: var(--theme-primary); }
  .dark .text-blue-400 { color: var(--theme-primary); }
  .bg-primary { background-color: var(--theme-primary); }
  .hover\:bg-primary-dark:hover { background-color: #083a75; } /* Bleu plus sombre au survol */
</style>